OL,7,FThe French Football Federation said on
OL,8,FTuesday it would file a legal
OL,9,Fcomplaint over "racially offensive and
OL,10,Fdiscriminatory remarks" that were made
OL,11,Fby Argentina players on Fernandez's
OL,12,FInstagram livestream following their
OL,13,FCopa America final win over Colombia.
OL,15,FThe footage appeared to show players
OL,16,Fparticipating in a chant about the
OL,17,FFrench national team, which dates back
OL,18,Fto when Argentina beat France in a
OL,19,Fpenalty shoot-out in the 2022 World
OL,20,FCup final.
