OL,7,FThe livestream was ended by Fernandez
OL,8,Fbefore the chant was finished.
OL,10,FFernandez put a statement on social
OL,11,Fmedia on Tuesday night, saying: "I
OL,12,Fwant to apologise sincerely for a
OL,13,Fvideo posted on my Instagram channel
OL,14,Fduring the national team celebrations.
OL,16,F"The song includes highly offensive
OL,17,Flanguage and there is absolutely no
OL,18,Fexcuse for these words.
