OL,7,F"I stand against discrimination in all
OL,8,Fforms and apologise for getting caught
OL,9,Fup in the euphoria of our Copa America
OL,10,Fcelebrations. That video, that moment,
OL,11,Fthose words, do not reflect my beliefs
OL,12,For my character. I am truly sorry."
OL,14,FFrench-Chelsea footballer Wesley
OL,15,FFofana reposted the video on his
OL,16,Fsocial media, writing "Football in
OL,17,F2024: uninhibited racism".
