OL,7,FChelsea released a statement on
OL,8,FWednesday morning, welcoming
OL,9,FFernandez's apology and announcing
OL,10,Fdisciplinary proceedings.
OL,12,F"Chelsea Football Club finds all forms
OL,13,Fof discriminatory behaviour completely
OL,14,Funacceptable," the statement read.
OL,16,F"We are proud to be a diverse,
OL,17,Finclusive club where people from all
OL,18,Fcultures, communities and identities
OL,19,Ffeel welcome.
